    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund guaranteed housing for armed forces veterans",
        "additional_details": "Following WW1, Lloyd George promised returning soldiers they would have homes that were fit for heroes.\r\n\r\nConflicts in recent history have led to a new wave of veterans caught up in the national housing shortage, who, through serving their country, have had life changing injuries and require additional housing needs. \r\n\r\nNot only that, any person willing to risk their life on the frontline to serve us should be repaid with a safe, warm home.\r\n\r\nWe call on the government to provide Homes for Heroes.",
        "background": "Provide councils with ringfenced funding to build a new generation of Homes fit for Heroes and guarantee armed forces veterans have a suitable home in return for their service.",
